<br>
In my humble opinion, I believe that there the system outlined in the W.W. books is entirely and apropriately functional as long as Status is NOT easily earned.<br>
<br>
I do have one related question:<br>
In the books, is there some discussion about the difference between City Status and Camarilla Status?  I don't have many of the books so I haven't been able to read up on it.<br>
