this is a game run by a storyteller.<br>
storyteller means gamemaster.<br>
for better or worse the person in charge, no matter what their title, has to make decisions for how things will function practically in game.  all good game systems, including WoD, back this up, the books all say these things in more than one place &quot;change things so they work for you&quot; and &quot;the storyteller is the boss&quot;.<br>
which means simply, that while everyone's input is valuable (why I asked John to post his and Kristen's ideas here) ultimately the combination of the current and incoming staff will decide how status works for this game.<br>
Santa Cruz's game and the mythical Santa Carla has indeed, always been non-standard, that is part of it's charm... if you want other than what Santa Cruz/Carla is, then you have to go elsewhere.<br>
